{"tid":1475660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"韓星第一人！ 金義聖表態：為香港祈禱","createTime":"2019-08-15T14:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T01:23:20.000Z","uid":35519,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"79b356ca88810f4a1e8cec54870d96e254975766","tid":1475660,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:25:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">韓星第一人！<br />\n《屍殺列車》金義聖表態：為香港祈禱 IG遭灌爆</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oiDY2Ki.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FoiDY2Ki.jpg&h=06db1f80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  ▲▼《屍殺列車》金義聖表態「為香港祈禱」。（圖／翻攝自金義聖IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/I4lIPf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FI4lIPf1.jpg&h=ed7f4be6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港示威活動持續升溫，南韓媒體近日也跟進報導，資深演員金義聖15日便在個人Instagram發文為香港應援「我們都在看著你，為你祈禱」，成為南韓第一位公開表態的藝人，當大批陸網友湧入他的IG攻擊時，他再度正面對抗：「習近平知道稅金浪費在這些人身上嗎？」勇於表達自己的心聲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6eqpI06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6eqpI06.jpg&h=943ea0ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  ▲金義聖被網友攻擊，他正面回應「近平先生知道稅金浪費在這些人身上嗎」。<br />\n  （圖／翻攝自金義聖IG）<br />\n<br />\n怎料，此舉引來網友不滿，湧入金義聖IG抗議「張紫妍事情解決了嗎」、「關你韓國人什麼事」，但也有其他網友為他說話「每個人都有言論自由」，面對負面謾罵，金義聖也不甘示弱回應「中國的網路暴力者為何在這種一點也不痛的地方攻擊呢？習近平先生知道稅金浪費在這些人身上嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n事實上，金義聖過去曾為MBC節目《探查企劃Straight》擔任主持人，揭露YG前社長梁鉉錫（楊賢碩）的陋習，勇於表達自己的意見，受到很多人推崇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7ZCUWpi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7ZCUWpi.jpg&h=4d12a1b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KTtopmZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKTtopmZ.jpg&h=2656aa63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wABV7RH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwABV7RH.jpg&h=151ea9c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/J4NWJxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJ4NWJxB.jpg&h=efc5da26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  ▲▼金義聖身為資深演員，合作的藝人星光熠熠。（圖／翻攝自金義聖IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Cp50pJd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCp50pJd.jpg&h=509fe96e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c18cec9b538549f20718c8e820873e5fc25ed0aa","tid":1475660,"uid":35519,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:28:06.000Z","msg":"面對五毛IG洗版<br />\n金義聖一夫當關<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VYHzEwF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVYHzEwF.png&h=50b4639f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14d4e677a5388fb3a6f0a35bf94b1f92443e9550","tid":1475660,"uid":180168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14755287a0f9907985c85bdc373db78cfe17df11","tid":1475660,"uid":35519,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:28:57.000Z","msg":"<em>lunatheboy</em><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>You are not alone. We stand with You.</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nwnLMcp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnwnLMcp.png&h=1729886c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36387cdd07e1cda3730578348fb0dd1904dfecf8","tid":1475660,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:29:27.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9bfa0bdcd